---
import BaseLayout from "../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
---

<BaseLayout title="Services">
  <section class="max-w-3xl mx-auto py-12 md:py-16 px-4">
    <h1
      class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-6 pb-2 border-b border-gray-200"
    >
      Analytical Chemistry Services
    </h1>

    <p class="text-gray-700 text-lg mb-10">
      I help companies understand and improve their products through
      expert-level analytical chemistry.
    </p>

    <ul class="space-y-8" role="list" aria-label="List of services offered">
      <li>
        <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-2">
          Quality Management System (QMS) Development
        </h2>
        <p class="text-gray-700">
          I assist laboratories in designing and implementing a robust Quality
          Management System aligned with ISO 17025 standards.
        </p>
      </li>

      <li>
        <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-2">
          Knowledge Management
        </h2>
        <p class="text-gray-700">
          I assist teams in capturing, organizing, presenting, and sharing
          critical information, ensuring valuable knowledge is retained and
          accessible for improved operational efficiency and decision-making.
        </p>
      </li>

      <li>
        <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-2">
          Method Development & Validation
        </h2>
        <p class="text-gray-700">
          Tailored analytical methods for complex matrices. Reliable,
          regulatory-ready, and robust.
        </p>
      </li>

      <li>
        <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-2">
          Continuous Improvement Initiatives
        </h2>
        <p class="text-gray-700">
          I help laboratories identify and implement continuous improvement
          opportunities that enhance efficiency, traceability, and quality.
        </p>
      </li>

      <li>
        <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-2">
          Spectroscopic & Chromatographic Analysis
        </h2>
        <p class="text-gray-700">
          Proficient in ICP-MS, ICP-OES, HPLC, GC, TGA, XRF. Accurate
          quantitative and qualitative interpretation.
        </p>
      </li>

      <li>
        <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-2">
          Data Interpretation & Reporting
        </h2>
        <p class="text-gray-700">
          Clear, concise reports with actionable insight. Optional review
          meetings included.
        </p>
      </li>

      <li>
        <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-2">
          Custom Consulting
        </h2>
        <p class="text-gray-700">
          Need a tailored solution? Let's discuss your lab or R&D goals.
        </p>
      </li>
    </ul>

    <div class="mt-12 text-center">
      <a
        href="/contact"
        class="inline-block bg-primary-blue hover:bg-primary-blue-dark text-white hover:text-white px-6 py-3 rounded-md font-semibold transition-colors duration-200 shadow-medium"
        aria-label="Go to contact page to work with Pablo"
      >
        Get in Touch
      </a>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
